  <brief_title>Gemcitabine and ISIS 2503 in Treating Patients With Advanced or Metastatic Cancer of the Pancreas</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase II Trial of Gemcitabine and ISIS 2503 in Patients With Locally Advanced or Metastatic Pancreatic Adenocarcinoma</official_title>
